  "description": {
    "zh": "呃...是啊，我有点事，你看起来和平时不一样。有什么我需要知道的吗？\n\n你知道么，其实我有个主意——带点酒来，我们晚点在仓库坐下来聊聊，你现在给人的感觉真的很奇怪，懂吗？好像有什么严重的事。你想说什么都可以告诉我，你知道你可以信任我。",
    "en": "Uhh... yeah I got something, you seem to behave differently than usual. Is there something I need to know?\n\nYou know what, actually I got an idea - Bring some drinks, we'll sit down at the depot later and discuss this, you give a really strange vibe right now, you know? Seems like something serious. You can tell me what you want to tell me, you know you can trust me."
  },
